>hello@example.com</p><p>(555) 123-4567</p><p>Madison, Wisconsin</p></div></section><section class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-ink\">Skills</h2><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Operations</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Project management</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Systems thinking</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Documentation</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Process design</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Stakeholder communication</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Data analysis</span><span class=\"rounded-md bg-mist px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink/75\">Vendor coordination</span></div></section></aside><div class=\"space-y-8\"><section class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-ink\">Highlights</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-3 text-ink/70\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-clay\"></span><span>Built durable operating systems across work, home, travel, and planning workflows.</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-clay\"></span><span>Experienced in cross-functional execution, stakeholder communication, and pragmatic process design.</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-clay\"></span><span>Comfortable moving from strategy to implementation with clear documentation and follow-through.</span></li></ul></section><section class=\"space-y-4\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-crisp\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Operations Lead</h2><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-clay\">2023 - Present</p></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/60\">Example Company</p><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-ink/70\">Designed team rituals, reporting workflows, vendor processes, and execution dashboards for a growing organization.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-crisp\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Project Manager</h2><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-clay\">2020 - 2023</p></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/60\">Previous Organization</p><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-ink/70\">Coordinated complex projects, improved handoffs, and kept timelines visible for internal and external partners.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-crisp\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Analyst</h2><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-clay\">2017 - 2020</p></div><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/60\">Earlier Team</p><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-ink/70\">Turned messy inputs into clear recommendations, models, and repeatable operating cadences.</p></article></section><section class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-ink\">Education</h2><div class=\"mt-4 text-ink/70\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-ink\">University Name</p><p>Degree or Certification</p><p>Year</p></div></section></div></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"border-t border-ink/10 bg-ink text-paper\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-10 text-sm sm:grid-cols-[1fr_aut